       routecodebelongto,
       servicename,
       servicetype,
       servicedescription,
       starttripnumber,
       orderonroute,
       busstopcode,
       busstopname,
       arrayindex,
       cumulatemileage,
       tripnumber,
       servicetypenumber,
       startdate,
       enddate,
       busstopcode_up,
       busstopname_up,
       busstopcode_down,
       busstopname_down,
       stoptype
